com.cube.storm.ui.model.list

Class List

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cube.storm.ui.model.Model

        • com.cube.storm.ui.model.list.List
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class List
extends ListItem
    A model which hosts an array set of child ListItem models. Used for displaying a sub set of lists within the list view.

    This is purely a data based model and is never used when displaying content in the list, instead the model is processed into 2 separate models, List.ListHeader and List.ListFooter
